Transcription.Text: Fruit. For fruit also this is the ideal planting season and work can continue at any time when the soil is in reasonable condition until the end of March. For a North wall I recommend a Morello cherry, for an East wall a plum or greengage and for a South or west-facing wall, a peach, nectarine or apricot.
